org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.client.builder

Class PrivilegeGrantInfoBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.client.builder.PrivilegeGrantInfoBuilder

  • public class PrivilegeGrantInfoBuilder
extends Object
    Builder for PrivilegeGrantInfo. The privilege is required. If not provided the grantor is assumed to be the current user. This is really intended for use by the HiveObjectPrivilegeBuilder.
